channel.title: Can someone give me a full explanation, please?
channel.description:
Sup, I have been away at making my server recently, and added my global objects just frequently, and have been testing with that. But, I noticed there's also a way to delete objects, but unfortunately, I don't know how, hence why I'm here making this post.
[i]Can someone give me a clear explanation on how to delete objects? I want to remake a town, thank you. I'm putting a lot of effort into this server, and this will help me greatly.[/i]
H E L P I S A P P R E C I A T E D !!! :)

item.title: Can someone give me a full explanation, please?
item.dc:creator: @Rudolph Rudolph
item.description:
@Rudolph wrote:

makeGlobalObject(####, ####, 6951, -1, 10);//Delete

Fill the # in with the coords, the 6951 deletes the object. Have fun
